                     <interp inst="t18281204-254-person2192" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a pawnbroker. I took in these trousers of the prisoner; he said he pawned them for his father for 9s.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18281204-254-person2193">
                  ROBERT 
                  TEASDALE
